title: Conversations about Race: Charles McPherson, Jazz Musician

description: This conversation was recorded with a permission as part of the series "Conversations about Race". The goal of the series is to draw attention to everyday stories of black people in America. Recorded in June 2020. In this conversation Charles and I talk about living in America in the 50s and 60s, social justice, everyday overt and subtle racism.
